"upgrade-to-&releasename;.typescript</tt> 来浏览这个文件。"

# type: <p></p>
#: ../en/release-notes.en.sgml:1344
msgid ""
"After you have completed the upgrade, you can stop <prgn>script</prgn> by "
"typing <tt>exit</tt> at the prompt."
