"如果您在 <prgn>script</prgn> 上使用了 <em>-t</em> 参数，您可以利用 "
"<prgn>scriptreplay</prgn> 程序来重新播放整个过程："

# type: <example></example>
#: ../en/release-notes.en.sgml:1353
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "# scriptreplay ~/upgrade-&releasename;.time ~/upgrade-&releasename;.script"
